dogData.greeting: Hi! I'm Macey. My ancestors are from Japan, but Me, I was born here in Denver. I am only 2 years old, but dont let that fool you I am very strong. Even though I have this cute and cuddly appearance, I hope to be a great huntress one day.

Well Hello There! I'm Max. I work hard and cuddle even harder. Some would call me a workaholic, but is it work when I'm having fun? I have a beautiful and playful exterior, but that is to mask my atheltic, agile, and durable build. I might be a tad bit shy around strangers, but I love playing with my friends.
